n%20a%20business%20climate%20where%20there's%20so%20much%20uncertainty.%20You%20can't%20produce%20coffee%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20There's%20no%20replacement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20industry%2C%20we%20were%20in%20denial%20when%20Trump%20was%20talking%20about%20tariffs%20last%20year%20or%20earlier.%20Even%20as%20we've%20gotten%20closer%2C%20we%20were%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20of%20course%2C%20he's%20going%20to%20make%20an%20exception.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20thought%20we%20were%20likely%20immune%2C%20so%20this%20has%20been%20something%20that%20is%20so%20disruptive.%20Importing%20a%20product%20that%20can%20only%20be%20produced%20outside%20of%20our%20borders%20is%20at%20the%20core%20of%20our%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a4da46e8-effa-4ebd-ae5d-e988cb26430c%5C%22%3EThe%20coffee%20industry%20was%20already%20in%20a%20shaky%20place%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225760%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Coffe%20being%20roasted%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f945873fe8d3928362dab7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWonderstate%20Coffee%20won%20Roaster%20Magazine's%20%26quot%3BRoaster%20of%20the%20Year%26quot%3B%20award%20in%202024.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wonderstate%20Coffee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Femma-chamberlain-coffee-expansion-plans-detailed-in-leaked-deck-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoffee%20market%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20getting%20zigzagged%20in%20every%20direction%20because%20there's%20so%20much%20uncertainty%20and%20volatility%20in%20everything%20right%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20last%20six%20months%2C%20the%20coffee%20industry%20has%20been%20dealing%20with%20historically%20high%20commodity%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20course%20of%20a%20few%20years%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20producers%20of%20coffee%2C%20Brazil%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-liberation-day-reciprocal-tariffs-speech-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVietnam%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20have%20been%20hit%20with%20climate%20disruptions.%20It's%20unprecedented.%20This%20affects%20everyone%2C%20from%20a%20roaster%20like%20us%20to%20huge%20brands%20like%20the%20Maxwell%20Houses%20and%20Starbucks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20there's%20been%20a%20supply%20crunch%2C%20which%20has%20pushed%20the%20price%20up%20due%20to%20it%20just%20being%20harder%20for%20farmers%20to%20grow%20the%20beans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d54b614-ce0f-473f-8cc1-cfd9c8bdd453%5C%22%3EIt's%20going%20to%20cost%20a%20lot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225104%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bags%20of%20wonderstate%20coffee%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f94609a466d2b74ab2f3ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223403%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWonderstate%20Coffee%20imports%20about%2014%20containers%20of%20coffee%20a%20year.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Wonderstate%20Coffee%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20coffee%20on%20the%20water%20right%20now%20that%20we%20think%20will%20be%20hit%20with%20tariffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEthiopia%20is%20our%20biggest%20African%20source.%20In%20Central%20America%2C%20it's%20Guatemala%2C%20and%20Peru%20is%20the%20main%20source%20in%20South%20America.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20I%20want%20to%20bring%20that%20coffee%20into%20the%20country%20and%20get%20it%20through%20customs%2C%20that%20tariff%20needs%20to%20be%20paid.%20I%20pay%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20deal%20in%20containers%2C%20which%20are%2040%2C000%20pounds%20of%20coffee.%20At%20%245%20per%20pound%2C%20I'd%20pay%20%24200%2C000%20for%20one%20container.%20If%20we%20start%20at%2010%25%2C%20the%20tariff%20would%20be%20%2420%2C000.%20We%20buy%20about%2014%20containers%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20we're%20looking%20at%20%24250%2C000%20to%20%24300%2C000%20of%20tariff%20impact.%20Some%20of%20that%2C%20no%20matter%20what%2C%20I%20have%20to%20absorb%20upfront.%20I%20have%20to%20finance%20it%2C%20I%20have%20to%20come%20up%20with%20the%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20have%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20afford%20that%20unexpected%20business%20cost.%20That%20means%20borrowing%20more%20money%2C%20which%20comes%20with%20interest%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20tying%20up%20my%20cash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f101236-239f-4879-a0ed-7d525bb5ffd2%5C%22%3EWhat%20now%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%2033%20coffee%20shops%20here%20in%20Wisconsin%2C%20around%20the%20state.%20We're%20in%20Whole%20Foods%20regionally%2C%20a%20bunch%20of%20Midwest%20grocery%20chains%2C%20and%20natural%20food%20cooperatives.%20We%20also%20sell%20to%20independent%20coffee%20shops%2C%20restaurants%2C%20and%20corporate%20campuses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETariffs%20are%20making%20me%20way%20more%20conservative%20in%20our%20outlook%20this%20year.%20We%20can't%20afford%20to%20invest%20in%20our%20people%2C%20invest%20in%20equipment%2C%20or%20invest%20in%20growth.%20We're%20pulling%20back%20on%20plans%20we%20had%20for%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20working%20with%20the%20two%20sides%20of%20the%20coffee%20world%3A%20we're%20working%20to%20empower%20farmers%20while%20providing%20consumers%20with%20some%20of%20the%20best%20coffees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20loyal%20customers%2C%20but%20as%20we%20increase%20prices%2C%20where%20and%20when%20do%20people%20stop%20drinking%20coffee%20or%20go%20somewhere%20else%3F%20The%20business%20environment%20is%20really%20dicey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20even%20know%20what%20the%20price%20of%20the%20bags%20that%20we%20put%20our%20coffee%20in%20is%20going%20to%20be.%20A%20lot%20of%20them%20come%20from%20Asia%2C%20and%20those%20tariffs%20are%20bouncing%20all%20over%20the%20place.%20Some%20come%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-retaliate-trump-trade-war-tariffs-soybeans-agriculture-two-sessions-2025-3%5C%