oil%20business%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20men%20stand%20with%20the%20olive%20tree.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f93878a466d2b74ab2ef7b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%C2%A0%3Cp%3EWildly%20Virgin%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENader%20Akhnoukh%20was%20living%20in%20Colorado%20and%20founded%20two%20successful%20tech%20startups.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20and%20his%20wife%20wanted%20a%20change%20of%20pace%20for%20their%20young%20family%20and%20moved%20to%20Portugal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAkhnoukh%20pivoted%20from%20tech%20to%20building%20Portugese%20olive%20oil%20business%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0which%20he%20said%20aren't%20so%20different.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20transcribed%20conversation%20with%20Nader%20Akhnoukh%2C%20an%20entrepreneur%20living%20in%20Portugal.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20began%20my%20career%20as%20a%20software%20design%20engineer%20in%201999%2C%20working%20at%20various%20technology%20companies%20in%20Boston%20and%20San%20Francisco.%20In%202008%2C%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20took%20a%20year%20off%20to%20travel%20the%20world%20and%20it%20was%20eye-opening.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202009%2C%20we%20relocated%20to%20Colorado%20and%20I%20founded%20a%20content%20management%20software%20company%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fnakhnoukh%2Fdetails%2Fexperience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKapost%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%20the%20CTO%20and%20grew%20the%20business%20for%20nine%20years%20until%20it%20was%20acquired%20by%20Upland%20for%20%2450%20million%20in%202019.%20As%20a%20major%20shareholder%2C%20I%20was%20happy%20with%20my%20share%20of%20the%20proceeds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20acquisition%2C%20I%20worked%20as%20the%20cofounder%20and%20CTO%20for%20Onward%2C%20an%20assisted%20transportation%20marketplace%20in%20California.%20I%20helped%20scale%20the%20business%20until%20it%20was%20acquired%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22118afb9d-e4ec-44b4-aed1-ce4d8d87eecc%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMoving%20to%20Portugal%20and%20considering%20my%20career%20options%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20lengthy%20career%20in%20tech%2C%20I%20felt%20ready%20for%20a%20change.%20At%2042%2C%20my%20family%20and%20I%20left%20Colorado%20for%20Portugal.%20My%20wife%20and%20I%20wanted%20a%20slower%20pace%20of%20life%20and%20better%20weather%20for%20our%20three%20sons%20ages%205%2C%208%2C%20and%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20applied%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.henleyglobal.com%2Fresidence-investment%2Fportugal%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Portugal%2520Golden%2520Residence%2520Permit%2520Program%2520(commonly%2520known%2520as%2520the%2Ccirculation%2520in%2520Europe%2527s%2520Schengen%2520Area.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPortugal%20Golden%20Residence%20Permit%20Program%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20a%20five-year%20residence-by-investment%20program%20for%20non-EU%20nationals.%20The%20process%20was%20fairly%20straightforward.%20We%20had%20to%20show%20that%20we%20were%20contributing%20to%20Portugal's%20economy%20through%20investment%2C%20real%20estate%20or%20donation.%20We%20ended%20up%20investing%20in%20a%20Portuguese%20real%20estate%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUpon%20arriving%20in%202020%2C%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20the%20culture%2C%20the%20people%2C%20and%20the%20food.%20Our%20sons%2C%20especially%20the%20younger%20two%2C%20quickly%20acclimatized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20still%20working%20with%20Onward%2C%20but%20I%20yearned%20to%20step%20away%20from%20screens%20and%20connect%20with%20something%20tangible%20that%20would%20ground%20me%20in%20my%20new%20home's%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExploring%20the%20culinary%20scene%20in%20Portugal%2C%20I%20learned%20how%20it%20revolves%20around%20olive%20oil.%20I%20began%20touring%20olive%20farms%20and%20researching%20the%20industry.%20I%20considered%20buying%20an%20olive%20farm%20but%20quickly%20realized%20local%20producers%20had%20perfected%20their%20craft%20over%20generations%20%E2%80%94%20expertise%20I%20couldn't%20replicate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20brainstormed%20business%20ideas%20with%20a%20former%20colleague%20back%20in%20Colorado%2C%20Riley%20Gibson.%20We%20had%20complementary%20skill%20sets%20and%20were%20keen%20to%20work%20together%20again.%20Neither%20of%20us%20had%20experience%20in%20agriculture%20or%20exporting%2C%20but%20Riley%20said%20he%20wanted%20to%20help%20me%20build%20something%20new.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220e0e6d2f-c47b-4f1b-9f5b-ccdbf04a3c71%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Portuguese%20love%20for%20olive%20oil%20inspired%20me%20to%20start%20a%20business%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202024%2C%20we%20officially%20launched%20an%20olive%20oil%20business%20called%20Wildly%20Virgin.%20We%20source%20oil%20from%20local%20growers%20and%20ship%20it%20to%20the%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20immersed%20myself%20in%20the%20local%20olive-growing%20regions%20and%20completed%20an%20olive%20oil%20sommelier%20program.%20I%20took%20lessons%20to%20improve%20my%20Portugese%20and%20get%20to%20an%20intermediate%20level%20to%20connect%20with%20producers%20who%20had%20limited%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20used%20the%20proceeds%20of%20my%20past%20business%20ventures%20to%20fund%20Wildly%20Virgin%20and%20live%20off%20while%20in%20Portugal.%20Luckily%2C%20the%20low%20cost%20of%20living%20compared%20to%20the%20US%20means%20my%20family%20and%20I%20have%20maintained%20our%20comfortable%20lifestyle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20take%20a%20salary%20from%20Wildly%20Virgin.%20I%20see%20a%20path%20to%20profitability%20this%20year%2C%20but%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20I'll%20be%20able%20to%20pay%20myself%20yet.%20The%20financial%20reality%20of%20running%20an%20olive%20oil%20company%20is%20very%20different%20from%20working%20in%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bc30a740-8608-43f1-b815-dde8123b2a5a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ETech%20and%20olive%20oil%20startups%20aren't%20that%20different%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20were%20surprised%20at%20my%20transition%20from%20tech%20to%20olive%20oil%2C%20but%20my%20background%20has%20proven%20valuable.%20The%20fundamentals%20of%20startups%20are%20the%20same.%20You%20have%20to%20deliver%20customer%20value%20and%20achieve%20product-market%20fit%2C%20whether%20it's%20software%20or%20olive%20oil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EScaling%20Wildy%20has%20demanded%20the%20same%20workload%20as%20my%20tech%20startup%20career.%20We%20establish%20quarterly%20objectives%2C%20track%20metrics%20and%20analyze%20operational%20challenges%20and%20market%20positioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20software%2C%20you%20can%20iterate%20weekly%2C%20constantly%20refining%20your%20offering.%20With%20olive%20oil%2C%20certain%20elements%20like%20marketing%20strategy%20can%20evolve%20quickly%2C%20but%20the%20core%20product%20development%20follows%20nature's%20timeline%3A%20there's%20only%20one%20olive%20harvest%20annually%2C%20demanding%20thoughtful%20planning%20and%20patience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20harvest%20occurs%20at%20year's%20end%2C%20so%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20year%20is%20operationally%20intensive%20as%20we%20test%20and%20select%20oils%2C%20source%20packaging%2C%20and%20coordinate%20with%20vendors%20for%20corks%20and%20labels.%20When%20summer%20arrives%20and%20our%20products%20become%20available%20for%20sale%2C%20we%20shift%20focus%20to%20marketing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ce5023e-eaa3-43c3-858b-6f53f6239a20%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20hope%20this%20endeavor%20will%20bridge%20the%20gap%20between%20my%20new%20and%20old%20experiences%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPortugal%20was%20a%20cultural%20shift%20for%20my%20family%2C%20but%20also%20an%20eye-opening%20career%20pivot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20business%20culture%20here%20operates%20on%20a%20different%20rhythm.%20I've%20spent%20an%20entire%20year%20traveling%20throughout%20the%20country%2C%20meeting%20producers%2C%20practicing%20Portuguese%2C%20and%20establishing%20connections.%20Relationships%20are%20paramount%20in%20business%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20States%2C%20networking%20is%20important%2C%20but%20on%20a%20lesser%20scale%20in%20the%20software%20world%2C%20where%20conversations%20happen%20remotely%20or%20behind%20the%20scenes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20I%20cherish%20living%20in%20Portugal%2C%20I%20felt%20somewhat%20disconnected%20from%20my%20professional%20network%20back%20in%20the%20States.%20I'm%20hoping%20a%20hands-on%20venture%20like%20Wildly%20Virgin%20helps%20bridge%20this%20gap%2C%20especially%20by%20working%20with%20RIley%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStepping%20away%20from%20technology%20has%20given%20me%20perspective%20on%20what%20made%20that%20industry%20special.%20I%20sometimes%20miss%20the%20nimbleness%20of%20software%20development.%20However%2C%20I%20can%20envision%20a%20future%20where%20we%20might%20blend%20both%20the%20tech%20and%20olive%20oil%20worlds%2C%20perhaps%20by%20incorporating%20a%20subscription%20model%20or%20innovation%20of%20our%20tech%20aspects%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20Portugal%20and%20building%20Wildy%20Virgin%20here%20is%20central%20to%20our%20company.%20I've%20fallen%20in%20love%20with%20this%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-us-portugal-olive-oil-business-2025-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1744449302000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f9389fa466d2b74ab2ef8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleft-us-portugal-olive-oil-business-2025-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tech%20founder%20Nader%20Akhnoukh%20left%20the%20US%20and%20moved%20his%20family%20to%20Portugal.%20He%20started%