e%20playing%20sports%20like%20polo%2C%20tennis%2C%20and%20golf.%20Forand%20says%20her%20Instagram%20is%20now%20filled%20with%20ads%20for%20women's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feastside-golf-apparel-breaking-barriers-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egolf%20fashion%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20they%20are%20just%20there%20for%20the%20looks%2C%20the%20surge%20of%20young%20people%20in%20the%20walled%20garden%20of%20the%20wealthy%20is%20having%20real%20consequences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20room%20for%20so%20many%20newcomers%2C%20the%20sports%20have%20had%20to%20evolve.%20Thompson%20says%20one%20of%20the%20coolest%20things%20about%20the%20tennis%20boom%20is%20seeing%20new%20fans%20create%20lasting%20change.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20that%20the%20younger%20fans%20and%20creators%20and%20journalists%20have%20pushed%2C%20the%20more%20the%20sport%20has%20to%20modernize%2C%20not%20only%20the%20way%20that%20it%20allows%20access%20but%20also%20the%20way%20it%20talks%20about%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EShe%20points%20to%20how%20the%20American%20tennis%20player%20Taylor%20Fritz's%20influencer%20girlfriend%2C%20Morgan%20Riddle%2C%20complained%20about%20some%20of%20the%20restrictions%20over%20what%20is%20shareable%20on%20social%20media%20%E2%80%94%20tournaments%20often%20ding%20creators%20for%20influencer-style%2C%20behind-the-scenes%20coverage%20of%20events.%20%26quot%3BThat%20actually%20has%20resulted%20in%20changes%20for%20what%20can%20be%20published%20from%20the%20grounds%20at%20a%20tournament%2C%26quot%3B%20Thompson%20says.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20golf%2C%20there's%20also%20been%20a%20culture%20clash.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-dont-like-country-clubs-membership-dues-evolution-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecountry%20clubs%3C%2Fa%3E%20offer%20discounted%20memberships%20specifically%20for%20those%20