%3E.%20While%20there's%20some%20bipartisan%20support%20for%20repurposing%20federal%20land%20for%20housing%2C%20Trump's%20vision%20would%20require%20local%20support%2C%20including%20from%20those%20concerned%20with%20environmental%20protection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AEI%20analysis%20focuses%20largely%20on%20metro%20areas%20in%20Western%20states%20like%20Nevada%2C%20Oregon%2C%20Colorado%2C%20and%20Idaho.%20The%20report%20envisions%20major%20new%20population%20centers%20in%20the%20outskirts%20of%20places%20like%20Las%20Vegas%3B%20Bend%2C%20Oregon%3B%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20Utah%3B%20and%20Grand%20Junction%2C%20Colorado.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20created%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faeihousingcenter.org%2Fhomesteading_2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einteractive%20map%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eshowing%20where%20they've%20determined%20the%20new%20cities%20could%20be%20built.%20The%20dark%20green%20locations%20shown%20below%20are%20the%20best%20fit%20for%20freedom%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20areas%20where%20we%20have%20plenty%20of%20land%2C%20why%20shouldn't%20we%20be%20using%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20Tobias%20Peter%2C%20co-director%20of%20AEI's%20housing%20center%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BThese%20cities%20with%20high%20prices%2C%20they%20have%20shown%20over%20time%20that%20they%20have%20little%20interest%20in%20promoting%20housing%20supply.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221754%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20showing%20where%20the%20American%20Enterprise%20Institute%20determined%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20cities%26quot%3B%20could%20be%20built.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67f7ecc6c6ad288d147dcd36%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAEI%20found%20that%20areas%20outside%20Western%20cities%20like%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20Salt%20Lake%20City%2C%20and%20Bend%2C%20Oregon%20would%20be%20best%20for%20new%20%26quot%3Bfreedom%20ci