20the%20Mumbai%20attacks%20-%20currently%20jailed%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-ranas-probe-reveals-elusive-dubai-man-who-knew-of-26-11-attacks-8145626%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_topscroll%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETahawwur%20Rana%20Probe%20Reveals%20Elusive%20%26quot%3BDubai%20Man%26quot%3B%20Who%20Knew%20Of%2026%2F11%20Attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%201997%2C%20Rana%20emigrated%20to%20Canada%2C%20accompanied%20by%20his%20wife%2C%20a%20practising%20physician%20named%20Samraz%20Rana%20Akhtar.%20There%2C%20he%20launched%20an%20immigration%20consultancy%20and%20later%20expanded%20into%20a%20halal%20meat%20business.%20This%20immigration%20business%20became%20a%20front%20to%20mask%20terror%20activities%2C%20with%20Headley%20posing%20as%20a%20consultant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20a%20medical%20degree%2C%20Rana%20joined%20the%20Pakistani%20army's%20medical%20corps.%20According%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20even%20after%20leaving%20service%2C%20he%20often%20wore%20military%20fatigues%20while%20meeting%20high-profile%20individuals%20associated%20with%20Pakistan's%20military%20intelligence%20wing%2C%20the%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI)%2C%20and%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20operatives.%20He%20is%20said%20to%20have%20regularly%20visited%20camps%20associated%20with%20terror%20outfits%20clad%20in%20uniform.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Sajid%20Mir%20Connection%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20Rana's%20regular%20contacts%2C%20investigators%20say%2C%20was%20Sajid%20Mir%2C%20a%20designated%20global%20terrorist%20and%20one%20of%20India's%20most%20wanted%20men.%20Mir%20allegedly%20acted%20as%20a%20principal%20handler%20during%20the%2026%2F11%20attacks%20and%20is%20accused%20of%20directing%20the%20siege%20of%20Mumbai's%20Chabad%20House%2C%20where%20six%20hostages%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20offered%20a%20%245%20million%20reward%20for%20information%20leading%20to%20Mir's%20capture.%20In%202022%2C%20India%20submitted%20an%20audio%20recording%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20where%20Mir%20was%20allegedly%20heard%20coordinating%20with%20the%20attackers%20during%20the%20siege.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EREAD%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%7C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftahawwur-rana-mumbai-attacks-in-tahawwur-rana-probe-an-isi-link-and-two-names-major-iqbal-sameer-ali-8138926%23pfrom-home-ndtv_premium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIn%20Tahawwur%20Rana%20Probe%2C%20An%20ISI%20Link%2C%20And%20Two%20Names%3A%20Major%20Iqbal%2C%20Sameer%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20that%20Rana%20has%20links%20not%20only%20to%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20but%20also%20to%20Harkat-ul-Jihad-al-Islami%20(HuJI)%2C%20another%20terror%20organisation.%20He%20reportedly%20visited%20their%20camps%2C%20sometimes%20accompanied%20by%20ISI%20officers%20and%20Pakistani%20military%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20ISI%20Link%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NIA%20sources%2C%20clad%20in%20Pakistani%20army%20uniform%2C%20Rana%20also%20met%20Major%20Iqbal%20-%20a%20suspected%20ISI%20official.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajor%20Iqbal%20-%20identified%20in%20a%202010%20US%20indictment%20as%20a%20serving%20ISI%20officer%20-%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20being%20the%20person%20who%20financed%2C%20directed%2C%20and%20micromanaged%20the%20reconnaissance%20missions%20conducted%20by%20David%20Headley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeadley%2C%20who%20pleaded%20guilty%20in%202010%20to%20avoid%20the%20death%20penalty%2C%20has%20described%20Major%20Iqbal%20as%20his%20primary%20ISI%20handler%2C%20part%20of%20a%20trio%20of%20agency%20officials%20who%20%26quot%3Brecruited%2C%20trained%2C%20and%20directed%26quot%3B%20him.%20In%20a%20testimony%20in%202011%2C%20Headley%20revealed%20over%2020%20email%20exchanges%2