0field%2C%20which%20have%20sparked%20criticism%20across%20the%20globe.%20Once%20considered%20to%20be%20an%20Asian%20powerhouse%2C%20the%20current%20Pakistan%20lot%20is%20chasing%20shadows%20of%20their%20former%20glory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarring%20their%20chaotic%20campaigns%20in%20the%20past%20ICC%20tournaments%2C%20Pakistan%20were%20truly%20exposed%20in%20the%20Champion%20Trophy%20organised%20on%20their%20home%20turf.%20The%20party%20organisers%20were%20the%20first%20to%20crash%20out%20of%20the%20tournament%20following%20back-to-back%20defeats%20against%20New%20Zealand%20and%20India%2C%20ending%20their%20title%20defence%20in%20the%20group%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20debacle%2C%20Pakistan%20toured%20New%20Zealand%20for%20five%20T20Is%20and%20three%20ODIs%20while%20keeping%20the%202026%20and%202027%20World%20Cups%20in%20the%20back%20of%20their%20minds.%20With%20a%20couple%20of%20new%20faces%2C%20Pakistan%20succumbed%20to%20a%204-1%20series%20defeat%20but%20remained%20optimistic%2C%20hoping%20to%20bounce%20back%20in%20the%20three%20ODIs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERizwan%20and%20Babar%20Azam%2C%20among%20the%20notable%20absentees%20in%20the%20T20Is%2C%20returned%20to%20the%20squad%2C%20but%20Pakistan's%20fate%20remained%20intact.%20An%20inexperienced%20New%20Zealand%20side%20whitewashed%20Pakistan%20by%20orchestrating%20a%203-0%20series%20triumph.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20suffered%20a%20lot%20of%20backlash%20after%20their%20unimpressive%20run.%20Amid%20the%20heavy%20criticism%20from%20fans%20and%20former%20cricketers%2C%20Rizwan%20urged%20the%20critics%20to%20offer%20solutions%20and%20guide%20them%20through%20the%20turbulent%20phase%2C%20leading%20to%20their%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20fine%20to%20criticise%20the%20team%2C%20but%20also%20guide%20us%20on%20how%20to%20improve.%20Recently%2C%20during%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%2C%20Wasim%20Akram%20gave%20us%20advice.%20I%20wanted%20to%20talk%20more%20with%20him