atment%2C%20which%20involves%20the%20water%20that%20is%20extracted%20from%20the%20lake%20weeds.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20water%20that%20comes%20out%20of%20the%20lake%20weeds%20is%20carefully%20treated%20to%20remove%20any%20harmful%20contaminants%20like%20heavy%20metals%2C%20organic%20pollutants%2C%20and%20other%20toxic%20substances%2C%20through%20our%20leachate%20treatment%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20treated%2C%20this%20water%20is%20safely%20returned%20to%20the%20soil%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20nourishes%20the%20land%20without%20causing%20any%20negative%20environmental%20impact.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comprehensive%20approach%20not%20only%20helps%20manage%20the%20invasive%20lake%20weed%20problem%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20sustainable%20agricultural%20practices%20by%20providing%20nutrient-rich%20organic%20manure%20while%20reducing%20carbon%20emissions%20and%20improving%20the%20health%20of%20the%20surrounding%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEmpowering%20the%20farmers%20of%20Kashmir%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20conversion%20has%20also%20benefitted%20around%202%2C500%20farmers%20in%20Kashmir%20so%20far%2C%20who%20now%20have%20access%20to%20organic%20manure%20at%20a%20lower%20price%20%E2%80%94%20Rs%2012%20per%20kg%2C%20compared%20to%20the%20Rs%2016%20per%20kg%20they%20were%20paying%20for%20chemical%20fertilisers%20brought%20in%20from%20other%20states%20like%20UP%20and%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20made%20an%20impact%20by%20enriching%20over%204%2C400%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20improving%20soil%20health%2C%20and%20supporting%20sustainable%20agriculture%20practices%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20the%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image