tch%20Foundation%20does%20a%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20for%20three%20years%20after%20which%20the%20forest%20is%20considered%20mature%20enough%20to%20thrive%20by%20itself%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F04%2Fcatch-foundation-plantation-9_11zon-1744205500-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-418905%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECatch%20Foundation%20does%20routine%20maintenance%20of%20the%20forest%20for%20three%20years%2C%20after%20which%20the%20forest%20is%20considered%20mature%20enough%20to%20thrive%20by%20itself%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20forest%20is%20thriving%20without%20intervention%2C%20the%20benefits%20are%20plenty.%20The%20most%20important%20of%20these%20is%20carbon%20sequestration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20single%20mature%20tree%20can%20absorb%20around%2048%20pounds%20of%20carbon%20dioxide%20per%20year.%20In%20doing%20so%2C%20trees%20lower%20the%20ambient%20temperatures%2C%20creating%20a%20more%20comfortable%20microclimate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESparking%20a%20positive%20revolution%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20trees%20absorb%20excess%20water%2C%20these%20forests%20reduce%20surface%20runoff%2C%20thus%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20flooding%20in%20heavy%20rainfall%20events.%20This%20success%20