-transform-barren-lands-in-india-creates-forests%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98She%20Was%20Widowed%20at%2016%2C%20Started%20a%20Pickle%20Biz%20at%2065%E2%80%99%3A%20This%20Daughter%20is%20Carrying%20Forward%20Her%20Amma%E2%80%99s%20Legacy%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHidden%20in%20a%20corner%20of%20the%20Internet%E2%80%99s%20archive%20is%20a%20tasty%20secret%20%E2%80%94%20one%20saut%C3%A9ed%20in%20cold-pressed%20oils%2C%20and%20enhanced%20with%3Cem%3E%20sendha%20namak%20%3C%2Fem%3E(Himalayan%20pink%20salt).%20A%20secret%20is%20only%20as%20good%20as%20its%20keeper.%20And%20so%2C%20we%20took%20it%20upon%20ourselves%20to%20trace%20Shyamlata%20Sihare%20down%20over%20three%20decades%2C%20two%20continents%2C%20and%20numerous%20cities%2C%20intent%20on%20discovering%20her%20journey%20of%20building%20%E2%80%98Old%20Fashioned%20Gourmet%E2%80%99%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%E2%80%98Aravali%20Foods%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F292787%2Fmasterchef-australia-sandeep-pandit-revives-traditional-kashmiri-pandit-recipes-indian-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20secret%20hinged%20on%20traditional%20Indian%20spices%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20time-tested%20cooking%20methods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%E2%80%99s%20pickles%2C%20%3Cem%3Epapads%3C%2Fem%3E%20(fried%20Indian%20snacks)%2C%20squashes%20and%20%3Cem%3Emangodis%20%3C%2Fem%3E(green%20gram%20fritters)%20have%20been%20breathing%20life%20into%20the%20dining%20tables%20of%20India%20since%201993.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20browse%20through%20Old%20Fashioned%20Gourmet%E2%80%99s%20fascinating%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F395076%2Fferns-pickles-pune-nataline-fernandes-jams-squashes-preserves-curry-pastes%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erepository%20of%20pickles%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20think%20l